# HaloSim cinematic pipeline (sidecar HS-2..HS-5) — heavy ray-traced staging.
# A long unattended sweep can dump 1000+ multi-MB BMP/PNG frames here before
# they are compiled (HS-5) into a single shippable clip. Never commit the raw
# staging; only the final compiled media + a few curated stills are tracked.
docs/calibration/halosim_outputs/_staging/
# BMP is always an intermediate in this repo (HaloSim emits BMP; we keep PNG).
# Note: ~25 legacy halosim *.bmp were committed before this rule and remain
# tracked — see the HS-2 doc note for the optional history-cleanup decision.
*.bmp

